<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to Hydraulisc</title>
    <meta property="og:title" content="Hydraulisc - Stay in the loop">
    <meta property="og:description" content="Welcome to Hydraulisc - Image Sharing Social Network like no other.">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/144374735">
    <!-- Unused Canonical and alternate "link"'s removed: https://www.html-easy.com/references/html-link-tag/ & https://ahrefs.com/blog/canonical-tags/ -->
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/144374735">
    <meta name="description" content="Stay in the loop, with Hydraulisc - where communities come together!">
    <meta property="og:site_name" content="Hydraulisc - Stay in the loop">
    <meta name="theme-color" content="rgba(33, 33, 33, 0.98)">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/welcomePage.css">
</head>
<body>
    <div class="body_main">
        <div class="home_wrapper">
            <div>
                <img src="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Hydraulisc/hydraulisc.github.io/main/assets/img/Hydraulisc.png" alt="Hydraulisc Logo" style="width: 200px; height: auto; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                <h1 class="home_heading">Stay in the loop, with Hydraulisc.</h1>
                <p class="home_subheading">Free, Open Source, Image Sharing Social Network, like no other.</p>
                <a style="background-color: #5667c7; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; color: white; text-decoration: none; text-transform: uppercase; font-weight: 600; font-size: 18px; transition: background-color 0.3s ease-in-out;" href="/register">Beta Private Test Access</a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="features_wrapper">
            <div class="features_text_container">
                <h2 class="features_text_title">Features</h2>
                <p class="features_text"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="features_grid_container">
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Free, Forever</h3>
                        <p>Hydraulisc is free, Open Source, and backed by donations. Absolutely no hidden fees or subscription costs.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Customizable, by design</h3>
                        <p>Hydraulisc is completely customisable. From custom themes to unique displays, the only limit is your imagination.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Self-Hostable</h3>
                        <p>Hydraulisc offers self-hosting options, with admin accounts, invite-only modes, and more in mind.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Privacy Focused</h3>
                        <p>No email is ever required, passwords are encrypted by default, no IP logging or general logging<sup>1</sup>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Share, like no other</h3>
                        <p>Hydraulisc users are allowed to create unlimited posts<sup>2</sup>, and share to their hearts content.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="feature_grid_area">
                    <div class="feature_grid_content">
                        <h3>Discriminators</h3>
                        <p>Ever wanted to boast your unique username? Hydraulisc allows up to 9998 users with the same username, separated by a discriminator<sup>3</sup>.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="open_source_banner">
            <h2 class="feature_list_title">Proudly Open Source</h2>
            <p>Hydraulisc is an open source project.<br>The code is available on <a href="https://github.com/Hydraulisc/foss-hydraulisc" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="text-decoration: underline !important;">GitHub</a>.</p>
            <div>
                <a href="https://ko-fi.com/SleepingAmi" target="_blank">
                    <img height="36" style="border: 0px; height: 36px;" src="https://storage.ko-fi.com/cdn/kofi5.png?v=6" alt="Donate on Ko-Fi.com">
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="version_display">
            <p>Hydraulisc v<%- version %></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>